OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy start with rain clearing
OL,6,Fto the north. Brightening up, with
OL,7,Fsunny spells but also the risk of
OL,8,Fshowers developing. These likely to be
OL,9,Fheavy, perhaps with thunder and hail
OL,10,Facross the south of the region.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers will gradually fade
OL,13,Fduring the evening; however, some may
OL,14,Flinger in the west. Remaining largely
OL,15,Fcloudy and generally mild.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FCloudy for many on bank
OL,18,Fholiday Monday but mostly dry with
OL,19,Fjust the odd shower. Perhaps a few
OL,20,Fbright spells emerging. Temperatures
OL,21,Fclose to normal for early May.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
